data.text:
Bad Schussenried, Germany. 04th Oct, 2014. Dolores und Sina (L) celebrate the announcement of the new Dirndl world record in the festival tent in Bad Schussenried, Germany, 04 October 2014. The brewery wants to set a new Dirndl world record. The current record was set at the Gaeubodenfest in Straubin in August 2014 with 2779 paricipants. Photo: FELIX KAESTLE/dpa/Alamy Live News
